data.description: Tastefully updated and expanded custom Cape on a quiet dead-end street in Red Bank! The open concept living room with gas fireplace, dining room and kitchen leave little to be desired. Sun-drenched main living space is showcased by wide plank Hickory floors and has an updated powder room. A large kitchen with stylish white cabinets, oversized island that seats six, stainless steel appliances, microwave drawer, farm sink and Quartz countertops creates the ideal gathering place. Primary suite is conveniently located on the first floor with two large closets and a gorgeous spa-like bathroom with a skylight, shower, soaking tub and spacious double vanity. Upstairs you will find 4 additional bedrooms all with generous closet space and a full bathroom. The partially finished basement adds a bonus room and plenty of storage! Relax and enjoy time outdoors in the large privacy fenced yard with well-appointed paver patio and aesthetically pleasing landscaping. Conveniently located close to downtown Red Bank, train to NYC, shopping, restaurants and the beach all while enjoying a charming neighborhood feel and highly desirable area schools.
